snippet.title: RAWMEN - Launch Trailer | Free To Play Food Fighter | Epic Games
snippet.description:
Jump into the messiest food fight ever with RAWMEN, now free to play exclusively on the Epic Games Store!

Download RAWMEN: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/rawmen-03f74e 

RAWMEN is a fast-paced, multiplayer action game where you engage in chaotic food battles. Take on friends and foes in the ultimate culinary showdown, using wacky weapons and deliciously destructive tactics. Prepare for epic food fights, hilarious moments, and endless fun!

Join the RAWMEN Community:
🌐 Discord: https://discord.gg/rawmen
🌐 X (formerly Twitter):https://x.com/rawmengame 
🌐 Epic Games Store: https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/rawmen-03f74e
